249
00:26:14,765 --> 00:26:17,432
Kau gadis yang sangat cantik, Margaretta.

250
00:26:18,515 --> 00:26:21,182
Kau harus memahami itu.

251
00:26:22,015 --> 00:26:24,640
Agar kau tahu apa yang kau tinggalkan.

252
00:26:26,224 --> 00:26:29,515
Biarkan dirimu merasakannya. Paham?

253
00:26:30,307 --> 00:26:31,349
Kau harus berani.

254
00:27:06,850 --> 00:27:07,850
Jadi...

255
00:27:08,850 --> 00:27:10,808
Untuk gadis paling berani.

256
00:27:10,975 --> 00:27:11,975
Ayo.

257
00:27:17,100 --> 00:27:18,433
Kakimu masih terasa?

258
